<%= render(partial: 'sun_template') %>

<div data-controller="sun" data-app-loaded-value="0" class="p-3 relative flex flex-row mt-5">

  <div class="border-r border-gray-darkest hidden md:block md:w-full p-5 ">
    <p class="p-5 mt-5 bg-purple-200 rounded">
      "There is no luck or misfortune, success or failure; everything is a vibration of the ether."
    </p>


    <p class="p-5 mt-5 bg-yellow-200 rounded">
      "The study of the vibrations of the ether (Tattvas) is indispensable. Remember that business, love, health. etc. are controlled by cosmic vibrations."
    </p>

    <p class="p-5 mt-5 rounded text-right text-blue-500">
      <a href="https://glorian.org/books/introduction-to-gnosis/lesson-three">Learn more @ Introduction to Gnosis</a>
    </p>


  </div>



  <div class="justify-center text-center w-full">

    <%#= render(partial: 'timer', locals: {controller: 'sun'}) %>
    <div class="w-full font-medium overflow-y-auto h-96" data-sun-target="timeNowStr">
      Wherever you go, no matter what the weather, always bring your own sunshine
    </div>


    <div class="text-xs w-full pt-10 hidden">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-1">
        <span>Sunrise: </span>
        <span data-location-target="sunrise"> </span>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-1">
        <span>Sunset: </span>
        <span data-location-target="sunset"> </span>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

  
</div>

<button
  data-location-target="btn"
  data-action="click->location#getLocation"
  class="bg-blue-500 rounded shadow-md font-light pb-2 pl-4 pr-4 pt-2 text-center text-white w-40">
  Get My Location
</button>
